@startuml sequence_zapping_liba4tv_v4
title Zapping - broadcast (liba4tv) - v4

actor User
box "Android app" #EBF5FF
  participant "Live TV App" as App
  participant "Broadcast TvInputService" as TIS
end box

box "liba4tv Java API (Android-facing wrapper)" #E8F5E9
  participant "ComediaRouteManagerControl" as ROUTE
  participant "DisplayControl" as DISP
  participant "ServiceControl" as SVC
  participant "ServiceListener\n(callback na TIS)" as SVCL
end box

box "Comedia native middleware" #FFF8E1
  participant "Comedia Core (MW)\nXSERV/Player + Table parser (PAT/PMT) + PTSM" as CORE
  database "Service & Mux DB\n(SList + PIDB)" as SDB
  participant "Comedia CHAL (TDAL)\nTDAL_DMD / TDAL_DMX / TDAL_AV / TDAL_DISP" as CHAL
end box

box "Platform / HAL - demonstration" #FFF3E0
  participant "Tuner SDK / Tuner HAL\n(Cuttlefish: .ts fajl kao izvor)" as TSDK
  participant "MediaCodec / AudioTrack" as AVDEC
end box

User -> App : Play channel 1
App -> TIS : onSetSurface(surface)
App -> TIS : onSetStreamVolume(0.0)
App -> TIS : onTune(channelUri)

TIS -> ROUTE : getLiveRoute(listIndex, serviceIndex, prevRouteId)
ROUTE --> TIS : liveRoute

TIS -> DISP : setVideoSurface(layer, SurfaceBundle)
DISP --> TIS : A4TVStatus

TIS -> SVC : registerListener(serviceListener)
TIS -> SVC : startServiceByTriplet(liveRoute, listIndex, serviceIndex, onid, tsid, sid)
SVC --> TIS : A4TVStatus

== Comedia native middleware ==

SVC -> CORE : pokreni playback na ruti (liveRoute)

note over CORE, SDB
 PAT/PMT su vec isparsirani tokom procesa instalacije servisa
end note

CORE -> SDB : ucitaj servis po tripletu (ONID/TSID/SID) iz Service & Mux DB
SDB --> CORE : PID-ovi servisa (video/audio PID, PCR PID, stream type)

CORE -> CHAL : TDAL_DMD - tune izvor (file/tuner) na ruti

CHAL -> TSDK : otvori protokol ('file') + otvori A/V i PCR PID filtere (PID-ovi iz PIDB)
TSDK --> CHAL : izvor zakljucan (locked) + PID-ovi dostupni

CHAL --> CORE : TDAL_DMX - A/V/PCR PID kanali spremni

CORE -> CHAL : TDAL_AV - otvori A/V kanale na PID-ovima (video/audio)
CHAL -> AVDEC : dekoduj video + audio; PCR/STC sync (lipsync)
note over AVDEC : demonstration: video+audio dekoder + display\nkomunicira sa HAL (VDEC/ADEC/GPU)
AVDEC --> CHAL : A/V tece, sinhronizovano
CHAL --> CORE : komponente spremne (PCR PID, A/V kanali aktivni)

CORE -> CHAL : TDAL_DISP - poveži dekodovani izlaz sa video surface-om (DisplayControl.setVideoSurface)
CHAL --> CORE : graphics/video plane spreman

== ServiceListener javlja TIS-u da je zap zavrsen ==
CORE --> SVC : servis pokrenut (interno)
SVC --> SVCL : channelChangeStatus(liveRoute, true, ServiceStateChangeError.OK)
SVCL --> TIS : channelChangeStatus(liveRoute, true, ServiceStateChangeError.OK)
SVC --> SVCL : safeToUnblank(liveRoute)
SVCL --> TIS : safeToUnblank(liveRoute)

TIS -> App : unmute (restore volume) + video vidljiv

== TIS cita osnovne info o servisu preko ServiceControl ==
TIS -> SVC : getServiceDescriptor(listIndex, serviceIndex)
SVC -> SDB : upit nad Service & Mux DB
SDB --> SVC : ServiceDescriptor podaci
SVC --> TIS : ServiceDescriptor (getName, getONID, getTSID, getServiceId)

TIS --> App : Service started -> Playback active

@enduml
